	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The "official" sample mapper (CNROM) is at <a href="http://www.nespowerpak.com/powerpakdev1.zip" class="postlink">http://www.nespowerpak.com/powerpakdev1.zip</a>. Be aware that you have to do quite a lot of rerouting to handle stuff like WRAM, even though readme.txt states "cnrom3 is the mapper logic.  only this block should need to be changed for other mappers". Nevertheless, I've based my mappers on this template.
<br />
<br />Loopy also posted his mapper sources <a href="http://nesdev.com/bbs/viewtopic.php?p=70610#70610" class="postlink">here</a> some time ago. These might be a better starting point nowadays.

		

		</td>
